HEADWORD: Homogonous
<hw>Ho*mog"o*nous</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/. See
<er>Homogeneous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having all the
flowers of a plant alike in respect to the stamens and
pistils.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

